  17,101,"And We had given/brought to Moses nine evidences/signs evidences, so ask/question Israel`s sons and daughters, when (he) came to them, so Pharaoh said to him: \"That I, I think/suspect you (E) you, Moses, (are) bewitched/enchanted"
